# Project Structure

This is a Next.js inventory management application built with TypeScript, Prisma ORM, and Tailwind CSS.

## Key Directories

- `/src/app`: Contains pages and API routes following Next.js App Router structure
- `/src/components`: Reusable React components
- `/src/lib`: Utility functions and helpers
- `/src/services`: Business logic and data access
- `/prisma`: Database schema and migrations

## Important Files

- [src/lib/utils.ts](mdc:src/lib/utils.ts): Contains core utility functions like date formatting and server-side margin calculations
- [src/lib/client-utils.ts](mdc:src/lib/client-utils.ts): Client-side utilities with `"use client"` directive
- [src/lib/prisma.ts](mdc:src/lib/prisma.ts): Prisma client instance for database operations
- [prisma/schema.prisma](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma): Database schema definitions
